{"type": "article", "id": 22691, "title": "翻转长桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-23T07:30:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122216QUySl5vB9zuigpFh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">法国的设计工作室 Atelier JMCA 要为巴黎的烹饪俱乐部 FOODLAB 的办公室设计一张工作桌，要求既可以是工作桌，切割台，也能容纳所有人围在一起吃饭。最简单的方式是让这张桌子可以旋转，首先将桌腿沿着中轴旋转到 120 度，就可使桌面翻转，实现木板和切割台的转换。桌子的侧边有插口满足电子产品的需要，它同时是加长桌的插口，两边扩展后使桌面的长度超过 4 米。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122214MPUpJkWyDlfu5IdA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122214u6oEGQCpwWLM3trl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222159wdGEqgFTAmt8XaJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122215c6FUC9np5jgOKLTu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}